    YOGA TEACHER TRAININGS
    ONLINE & IN BALI
    Program Overview

    You want a Teacher Training Course that offers authentic Yoga and really deepens your practice & knowledge?

    Are you looking for a professional program with heart-centered teachers who actually embody the teachings and share their wisdom in a relatable way? 

    ​

    Yoga schools can offer lots of alignment details & terminology, without presenting Yoga in a straightforward way that is deep, yet simple at the same time.

    ​

    At MILANYAM, we take the authentic essence of breath-based Yoga and present it in a way that empowers you to become a confident self-practitioner, that deepens your knowledge & experience of the wisdom of Yoga, and enables you to share your love of Yoga with others.

    ​
